          practice: "Packet Tracer: two test runs. (1) Both desirable — forms. (2) Desirable + auto — forms. Pair each with the LACP equivalent lab to cement the mode mapping. Compare 'show etherchannel summary' — the only difference is the protocol column (PAgP vs LACP); the flags and behavior are identical.",
