          meta: "Jeremy's IT Lab Day 22. Wendell Odom OCG Chapter 10. Exam will test the distinction directly: 'which guard err-disables on any BPDU?' = BPDU Guard. 'Which only reacts to superior BPDUs?' = Root Guard. 'Which recovers automatically?' = Root Guard."
